<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>当選結果 | 友だち追加</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Hiragino Sans", "Yu Gothic", "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.2), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.14), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #111827 45%, #1f2937 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px 0;
    }
    .card {
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 42px 28px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.36);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .glow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: -60px auto auto -60px;
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.28), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .result-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.35);
      color: #fde68a;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 20px 0 14px;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 7vw, 72px);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .lead {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-size: clamp(16px, 2.2vw, 20px);
    }
    .panel {
      margin: 28px auto 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      text-align: left;
    }
    .panel h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    .panel p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      line-height: 1.85;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .cta {
      margin-top: 28px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 60px;
      padding: 0 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #111827;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fde68a, #facc15);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.24);
    }
    .note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap hero">
    <section class="card">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <div class="result-chip">WINNER RESULT</div>
      <h1>ご当選<br>おめでとうございます</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        エントリーの確認が完了しました。<br>
        詳細の受け取り・次の案内は、下のボタンから
        <strong>LINEのトーク画面</strong>をご確認ください。
      </p>

      <div class="panel">
        <h2>次の流れ</h2>
        <p>
          1. 下のボタンからLINEを開く<br>
          2. トーク内の案内メッセージを確認する<br>
          3. 必要事項がある場合は返信し、手続きを進める
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta">
        <a class="btn" href="https://lin.ee/UgmaEbq">LINEで詳細を確認する</a>
        <a href="https://lin.ee/UgmaEbq"><img src="https://scdn.line-apps.com/n/line_add_friends/btn/th.png" alt="เพิ่มเพื่อน" height="36" border="0"></a>
      </div>

      <p class="note">
        ※ 本ページは結果案内用のLPです。<br>
        ※ 最終的な詳細・対応内容はLINE上の案内に準じます。
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
